extendedInfo.description: The 2013 NASPA Annual Conference is the premiere gathering place for student affairs administrators in higher education and is an amazing professional development opportunity. This year's theme is "Bold Without Boundaries" and will be reflected in ground breaking keynote speeches and educational sessions by culture icons, thought leaders, and other student affairs professionals. By attending you?ll forge relationships with your peers, get hands on experience with new products, and enjoy three and a half days of enrichment!Keywords: NASPA, Student Affairs, Higher Education, Orlando, Annual Conference, 2013
